   <S PAR='128' RSNT='1' SNO='128'>After you hear it, God will immediately give you a test to determine whether or not the word is yours.</S>
   <S PAR='129' RSNT='1' SNO='129'>Although you have heard a word and have some scriptural knowledge about that particular word, you have not paid the price to join yourself to the word; you have not denied yourself and accepted the cross in your experience.</S>
