   <S PAR='156' RSNT='1' SNO='156'>This is why He had to give them the cross, to expose their true self.</S>
   <S PAR='157' RSNT='1' SNO='157'>Then one day, they found that they had a problem with God and began to argue with Him.</S>
   <S PAR='158' RSNT='1' SNO='158'>I am afraid that many Christians have already had an argument with God and developed a problem with God.</S>
   <S PAR='159' RSNT='1' SNO='159'>One day you will find that God has not dealt with you according to your expectation.</S>
   <S PAR='160' RSNT='1' SNO='160'>You will find that God has not done what you expected.</S>
   <S PAR='161' RSNT='1' SNO='161'>You hope that God will do things one way, but He decides to do them another way.</S>
