   <S PAR='172' RSNT='1' SNO='172'>Every argument is followed by failures.</S>
   <S PAR='173' RSNT='1' SNO='173'>If God has failed, and you have won, you will surely become dry.</S>
   <S PAR='174' RSNT='1' SNO='174'>Therefore, every time you go to God, the cross is your test; it will determine if your life is rich or dry.</S>
   <S PAR='175' RSNT='1' SNO='175'>I know that many of you have argued with God this way.</S>
   <S PAR='176' RSNT='1' SNO='176'>I also know that many of you are still in the midst of arguments and have not settled them yet.</S>
