   <S PAR='182' RSNT='1' SNO='182'>Never think that you have won forever just because you have gained what you desired.</S>
   <S PAR='183' RSNT='1' SNO='183'>This is really a pronouncement that your life is drying up and that your living is falling fast.</S>
