   <S PAR='188' RSNT='1' SNO='188'>Brothers and sisters, if you are in the middle of a dispute with God and the matter is not yet settled, if there is an unresolved problem between you and God, and if you are still not clear concerning the will of God, I can frankly say that this is very dangerous.</S>
   <S PAR='189' RSNT='1' SNO='189'>You have to be very careful.</S>
   <S PAR='190' RSNT='1' SNO='190'>If you blame God or despise His arrangement, you will fail right then.</S>
