   <S PAR='192' RSNT='1' SNO='192'>Therefore, God will not allow us to hear a message or offer a consecration and let the matter be concluded.</S>
   <S PAR='193' RSNT='1' SNO='193'>Every time you say that you will not fail, that you will be an obedient Christian, and that you will follow the Lord to walk in the way, the Lord will test you immediately.</S>
   <S PAR='194' RSNT='1' SNO='194'>The Lord will not allow you to bear the name of being obedient to Him, without first testing you.</S>
