   <S PAR='197' RSNT='1' SNO='197'>Since God cannot trust in you, He allows affliction and persecution pertaining to His word to come upon you and test you to see how you will react.</S>
   <S PAR='198' RSNT='1' SNO='198'>Then you will prove if you really are for God or if you were merely making a superficial confession.</S>
   <S PAR='199' RSNT='1' SNO='199'>At the time of your trial, you may not praise Him as much as before.</S>
   <S PAR='200' RSNT='1' SNO='200'>During those times, you may not be as clear about God as before.</S>
