   <S PAR='207' RSNT='1' SNO='207'>She then asked, What if the Lord does not want you to work for Him?</S>
   <S PAR='208' RSNT='1' SNO='208'>I answered, He surely wants me to work for Him.</S>
   <S PAR='209' RSNT='1' SNO='209'>I know that.</S>
   <S PAR='210' RSNT='1' SNO='210'>She then began to read with me the passage in Matthew 15 concerning the Lord feeding the four thousand with the seven loaves and the fish.</S>
