   <S PAR='226' RSNT='1' SNO='226'>Therefore, allow me to say the same thing to you now: If you do not want to be broken by the Lord, please do not put yourself into His hand.</S>
   <S PAR='227' RSNT='1' SNO='227'>This is where the problem lies with many people.</S>
   <S PAR='228' RSNT='1' SNO='228'>When they hear the teachings concerning overcoming, they are very happy and say, God, I will consecrate everything I have to you.</S>
   <S PAR='229' RSNT='1' SNO='229'>But when God begins to break them, they cry, Oh, I did not expect to encounter such things.</S>
